This paper is about evolving neural networks, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also discusses the interplay between evolution and learning, which is relevant to robotics and control systems (cs.RO and cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.RO (Robotics), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
